# Only .gs files and the manifest belong in Apps Script.
#
# Without this, `clasp push` uploads tests/*.js as Apps Script source. Those are
# node scripts — their top-level require() throws as soon as ANY function in the
# project runs, so the whole project breaks and the error points somewhere
# unrelated. Ignore everything, then re-admit only what Apps Script can execute.

**/**

!*.gs
!appsscript.json
